| Package | Version | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `fastapi` | 0.104.1 | Web framework |
| `uvicorn[standard]` | 0.24.0 | ASGI server |
| `sqlalchemy` | 2.0.23 | ORM |
| `alembic` | 1.12.1 | Migrations |
| `psycopg2-binary` | 2.9.9 | PostgreSQL driver |
