> [!NOTE]
> Custom fonts (Rajdhani, Outfit) are listed in `pubspec.yaml` but commented out. Font files need to be placed in `assets/fonts/` and the pubspec section uncommented to activate them.

### 4.8 Build Analysis Files

The frontend directory contains numerous large log files (`build_log_fixed_braces.txt` at 853 KB, etc.) that are **development artifacts** and should not be committed to version control. These suggest significant build troubleshooting history.

