## 8. Known Technical Issues & Observations

| # | Severity | Issue | Location |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | 🔴 High | `ai.py` and `workouts.py` API endpoints are empty stubs — not registered in router | `backend/app/api/v1/endpoints/` |
| 2 | 🔴 High | `flutterwave_service.py` is empty — Flutterwave backend service not implemented | `backend/app/services/payments/` |
| 3 | 🟡 Medium | `sendgrid` package not in `requirements/base.txt` despite `email_service.py` using it | `backend/requirements/base.txt` |
| 4 | 🟡 Medium | Dual Alembic setup (root + backend) risks migration confusion | Root & `backend/alembic/` |
| 5 | 🟡 Medium | Custom fonts (Rajdhani, Outfit) commented out in `pubspec.yaml` | `frontend/pubspec.yaml` |
| 6 | 🟡 Medium | Many large build log files in `frontend/` root — should be in `.gitignore` | `frontend/*.txt` |
| 7 | 🟢 Low | `permission_handler: any` and `path: any` use unconstrained version specs | `frontend/pubspec.yaml` |
| 8 | 🟢 Low | `CALORIES_PER_REP` constants are hardcoded in config rather than database-driven | `backend/app/config.py` |
| 9 | 🟢 Low | `ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRE_MINUTES` is 10080 (7 days) in config but Docker Compose sets it to 30 | Config vs. Docker mismatch |

